263
00:16:33,761 --> 00:16:35,461
( screams )
Uh!

264
00:16:36,810 --> 00:16:38,090
King Sombra...

265
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:42,550
<i>My crystal slaves... </i>

266
00:16:42,551 --> 00:16:44,551
( whimpering )

267
00:16:46,035 --> 00:16:47,800
( grunts )

268
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:50,140
