269
00:16:50,290 --> 00:16:51,720
I got the Crystal Heart!

270
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:55,920
<i>That is mine! </i>

271
00:16:55,921 --> 00:16:58,587
( ominous theme playing )

272
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:07,770
Spikey-Wikey!

273
00:17:24,328 --> 00:17:25,674
KING SOMBRA: 
Huh?

274
00:17:29,537 --> 00:17:30,395
CRYSTAL PONY:
Who is that?

275
00:17:30,395 --> 00:17:32,890
Behold! The Crystal Princess!

276
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:36,200
The Crystal Heart has returned.

277
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:40,750
Use the light and love within you
to ensure that King Sombra does not.

278
00:17:52,450 --> 00:17:57,760
<i>What?
No... No! Stop! </i>

279
00:18:05,745 --> 00:18:08,700
( majestic theme playing )

280
00:18:08,701 --> 00:18:10,101
RARITY: 
Ooh! ( laughs )

281
00:18:20,282 --> 00:18:24,574
( screams )

282
00:18:25,051 --> 00:18:28,000
( uplifting theme playing )

283
00:18:45,962 --> 00:18:48,900
( all cheering )

284
00:18:51,990 --> 00:18:54,300
( sighs )
Good job, Spike.

285
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:03,240
RARITY:
I do so wish it was permanent.

286
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:06,000
Did you see how
my mane just absolutely sparkled?

287
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:09,050
But... good things are better
when they're a rarity.

288
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,651
Oh! 
( giggles )

289
00:19:10,650 --> 00:19:12,030
SHINING ARMOR:
Everything's gonna be okay.

290
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:16,750
You've gotta stop saving my rump like this,
it's starting to get embarrassing.

291
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:21,380
Wasn't me who saved you in the end.
It was Spike.

292
00:19:21,530 --> 00:19:24,400
