give me a new test.

294
00:19:31,910 --> 00:19:35,980
Keep it together, buddy...
gotta stay strong... for Twilight...

295
00:19:36,190 --> 00:19:37,680
It's beautiful.

296
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:40,470
I wish it had been me
who ultimately made it so.

297
00:19:41,100 --> 00:19:42,300
But it wasn't.

298
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:44,360
Twilight,
as I understand it,

299
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:46,690
Spike brought Princess Cadance
the Crystal Heart

300
