307
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:17,150
Keep it together, buddy...
gotta stay strong... for Twilight...!

308
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:21,100
I passed!

309
00:20:21,101 --> 00:20:23,910
( all cheer )

310
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:29,730
<i>You were prepared to do your best </i>

311
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:33,370
<i>Had what it takes to pass the test </i>

312
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:36,810
<i>All those doubts you can dismiss </i>

313
00:20:36,970 --> 00:20:42,350
<i>Turns out
you were prepared for this! </i>

314
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:45,550
<i>You clearly have just what it takes </i>

315
00:20:46,500 --> 00:20:48,920
<i>To pass the test with such high stakes </i>

316
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:53,470
<i>We knew for sure you would prevail </i>

317
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:57,020
<i>Since when does
Twilight Sparkle ever fail? </i>

318
00:20:57,750 --> 00:21:01,230
<i>All those doubts that you can dismiss </i>

319
00:21:01,380 --> 00:21:04,650
<i>Trust yourself and you cannot miss </i>

320
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:06,420
<i>Turns out you were </i>

321
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:08,480
<i>Turns out I was </i>

322
00:21:08,630 --> 00:21:10,140
<i>Turns out you were </i>

323
00:21:10,290 --> 00:21:12,240
<i>Turns out I was </i>

324
00:21:12,390 --> 00:21:20,030
<i>Turns out you were prepared for this!</i>

325
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:28,250
( laughs nervously )
Yeah, I knew everything was gonna be fine.

